## ðŸ“Š Statistical Significance
- **T-test**: GPA is significantly lower in high-addiction vs low-addiction groups (p < 0.05).  
- **Chi-square**: Addiction level strongly associated with sleep quality (p < 0.05).  
- **ANOVA**: GPA differs significantly across screen-time groups (p < 0.05).  

